      Things happen
   =20
 =20
When a Hacker Calls: How Robinhood Fell Victim to a  Vishing Raid. China Ca=
sh Flowed Through  Congo Bank to Former President=E2=80=99s Cronies. Wall S=
treet Grudgingly Allows Remote Work as Bankers Dig In. U.K. Looks to Compet=
e on Financial Regulation. Oil=E2=80=99s  Black Friday: Algos and Options T=
urn a Tumble Into a Crash. Binance  Reopens Dogecoin Withdrawals After Musk=
 Spat With CEO. Jack Dorsey Steps Down as  Twitter CEO, Replaced by CTO Par=
ag Agrawal. The Evergrande Blueprint Worked for Other Chinese Developers, U=
ntil It Didn=E2=80=99t. The Great  Huckleberry Supply Crunch. Macau Casino =
Stocks Sink After Police Arrest City=E2=80=99s  Junket King. Matthew  McCon=
aughey Says He Won=E2=80=99t Run for Texas Governor in 2022. Nordea Retract=
s  Vaccine Conspiracy-Fueled Research Note. Congrats Claire!If you'd like t=
o get=C2=A0Money=C2=A0Stuff=C2=A0in handy email form, right in your inbox, =
please=C2=A0subscribe at this link. Or you can subscribe to Money Stuff and=
 other great Bloomberg newsletters here. Thanks![1] The longer-term perform=
ance of IPOs is less great, but if you can buy at the IPO price you can fli=
p on the first day and capture that pop.=C2=A0[2] From the prospectus: =E2=
=80=9CWe intend to form and register Pershing Square SPARC Holdings II, Ltd=
., a SPARC that will pursue a subsequent business combination after the com=
pletion of SPARC=E2=80=99s business combination. We expect to distribute 24=
4,444,444 SPARC II Tontine SPARs (=E2=80=98SPAR2s=E2=80=99) only to those S=
PAR holders who exercise to receive stock in SPARC=E2=80=99s initial busine=
ss combination. The distribution of SPAR2s will provide additional value to=
 exercising SPAR holders, and to the extent that this increases the trading=
 price of SPARs prior to closing, it will increase the likelihood that all =
or substantially all SPARs are exercised. By providing free SPAR2s to exerc=
ising holders, we provide more value to exercising SPAR holders, increasing=
 the probability of SPARs being exercised, and thereby increasing transacti=
on certainty for our business combination partner. We intend to use this sa=
me approach for Pershing Square SPARC Holdings III, Ltd. and thereafter.=E2=
=80=9D[3] And to SPAC pitches, but the old theory that SPACs offered certai=
nty of proceeds is no longer particularly true.=C2=A0[4]=C2=A0The SPARC fil=
ing says:=C2=A0=E2=80=9CNo later than December 9, 2021, we expect that the =
SEC will either approve the rule, disapprove the rule, or institute proceed=
ings to determine whether the rule change should be disapproved. =E2=80=A6 =
The NYSE=E2=80=99s rule proposal submission and public comments can be view=
ed on the SEC=E2=80=99s website at https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/=
click/25866447.270656/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9jb21tZW50cy9zci1ueXNlLTIwM=
jEtNDUvc3JueXNlMjAyMTQ1Lmh0bS4/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB3c8796bf Of the app=
roximately 168 public comments published on the SEC=E2=80=99s website, an o=
verwhelming majority express support for the proposed rule. =E2=80=A6 Howev=
er, there is no guarantee that this or a similar listing rule will be appro=
ved, or that our company will comply with and be approved for listing on th=
e NYSE pursuant to any such rule. If our SPARs cannot be listed on the NYSE=
, they would trade on the =E2=80=98over-the-counter=E2=80=99=C2=A0market, w=
hich may present significant risks to the holders of SPARs, including lower=
 availability and efficiency of market price quotations, significantly less=
 liquidity, increased trading costs, the absence of certain corporate gover=
nance protections, and the applicability of state securities laws that coul=
d result in restrictions on the sale of our SPARs.=E2=80=9D
