=E2=80=93 a full-length male nude =E2=80=93 at auction. He then received a =
call from the British artist, asking to buy it from him. The two men did no=
t know each other, and the collector politely refused, as he liked the pict=
ure.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Three days later, he claims he receive=
d another call from a now furious Freud who told him that, unless he sold i=
t to him, he would deny having painted it.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=
