 To his dismay, the Freud estate subsequently refused to authenticate Stand=
ing Male Nude =E2=80=93 and that could have been the end of a sad tale for =
the collector. =E2=80=A6</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In 2016, an early =
Freud picture was attributed to the artist, despite his own denials that he=
 painted it. Philip Mould=E2=80=99s BBC show Fake or Fortune? uncovered evi=
