rtist had apparently refused to acknowledge the work because it was origina=
lly owned by Denis Wirth-Miller, an artist with whom Freud had a long-runni=
ng feud.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">So, one, on a persona=
l level, that=E2=80=99s great: The man devoted his life to art, but he neve=
